'''桥粒黏蛋白'''（{{lang-en|desmoglein}}）是由蛋白質[[DSG1|DSG1]]、[[DSG2|DSG2]]、[[DSG3|DSG3]]和[[DSG4|DSG4]]組成的橋粒[[钙黏蛋白|钙黏蛋白]]家族。它們在连接细胞的[[橋粒|橋粒]]的形成中發揮作用。<ref>{{Citation|last=Kline|editor-first=Vann|last2=Mohler|access-date=2020-10-23|doi=10.1016/b978-0-12-417027-8.00004-0|language=en|publisher=Academic Press|series=Functional Organization of Vertebrate Plasma Membrane|editor-last=Bennett|first=Crystal F.|pages=121–158|volume=72|work=Current Topics in Membranes|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/B9780124170278000040|date=2013-01-01|title=Chapter Four - Evolving Form to Fit Function: Cardiomyocyte Intercalated Disc and Transverse-Tubule Membranes|first2=Peter J.|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030030657/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/B9780124170278000040|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 病理学 ==
桥粒黏蛋白靶向[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]][[天疱疮|天疱疮]]。<ref name="pmid16211092">{{cite journal|title=Pemphigus foliaceus IgG causes dissociation of desmoglein 1–containing junctions without blocking desmoglein 1 transinteraction|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-clinical-investigation_2005-11_115_11/page/3157|date=November 2005|journal=J. Clin. Invest.|issue=11|doi=10.1172/JCI23475|volume=115|pages=3157–65|pmc=1242188|pmid=16211092|vauthors=Waschke J, Bruggeman P, Baumgartner W, Zillikens D, Drenckhahn D}}</ref><ref name="pmid12705872">{{cite journal|title=Desmoglein 4 in hair follicle differentiation and epidermal adhesion: evidence from inherited hypotrichosis and acquired pemphigus vulgaris|date=April 2003|journal=Cell|issue=2|doi=10.1016/S0092-8674(03)00273-3|volume=113|pages=249–60|pmid=12705872|vauthors=Kljuic A, Bazzi H, Sundberg JP, etal|doi-access=free}}</ref><ref name="pmid19456767">{{cite journal|title=Autoantibodies against desmocollins in European patients with pemphigus|url=https://zenodo.org/record/3436428|date=May 2009|journal=Clin. Exp. Dermatol.|issue=8|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2230.2009.03241.x|volume=34|pages=898–903|pmid=19456767|vauthors=Müller R, Heber B, Hashimoto T, etal|s2cid=774308}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

桥粒黏蛋白是一种钙黏蛋白，这种[[跨膜蛋白|跨膜蛋白]]可与其他钙黏蛋白結合，形成一种被稱為細胞間橋粒的连接。这些桥粒黏蛋白将细胞结合在一起，但是当机体开始产生针对桥粒黏蛋白的[[抗体|抗体]]时，连接处会分解，从而导致[[水泡|水泡]]或[[囊泡|囊泡]]的形成。<ref>A Clinician's Guide to Pemphigus Vulgarishttp://www.springer.com/gp/book/9783319677583 {{Wayback|url=vulgarishttp://www.springer.com/gp/book/9783319677583 |date=20190617231629 }}</ref><ref>Bolognia JL, Jorizzo JL, Schaffer JV, editors. Dermatology. 3rd ed. Philadelphia: Elsevier
